videos.description: Matisse Thybulle gathers the rock and knocks down the 3-pointer after a great defensive play from Joel Embiid.
videos.headline: Embiid steals the rock and Matisse Thybulle drains the 3 from deep

videos.description: Cameron Johnson hustles down the court and soars through the paint for the big-time block.
videos.headline: Cameron Johnson elevates for the massive rejection

videos.description: Devin Booker hauls in the absolute dime from Chris Paul and lays it in to tie the game at 46-46.
videos.headline: CP3 rifles a dart to Devin Booker for a Suns bucket

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey drives into the paint and dishes a no-look dime to Joel Embiid for the bucket to extend the 76ers' lead.
videos.headline: Tyrese Maxey with the sweet no-look dime to Embiid for the bucket

videos.description: Chris Paul drives towards the basket and knocks down the floater for the Suns.
